# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
we are using bfs here.

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
we start bfs from the given node (row,col).
now we check it's neighbours if it is has same color then we push in queue and increment the counter .
if value of counter is less than 4 than we have to recolor to thisw node with given color.

# Complexity
