The answer can be within a range so we will apply Binary Search on ANSWER.

# Approach
Initialize low and high with minimum and maximum value which answer can be possible.

Now Apply Simple Binary Search on ANSWER code and write the feasible condition.

In feasible condition we will take a variable time and calculate the total time taken for the speed which we calculated using mid.
Return true if required time is <= hour.

